{"tid":1828604,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳茂波: 是否派錢意見分歧","createTime":"2020-01-18T04:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T10:16:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0122059ac04af06d728eaafaa501b3d42bb89e0f","tid":1828604,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:06:08.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波在本台節目《眾言堂》表示，對於是否派錢的意見分歧，作為財政司司長都希望市民開心，但負責公共資源要負責任，有人認為資源應用在有需要的人身上，派錢不是恰當地運用資源，他會多聽意見。<br />\n<br />\n至於消費券問題，陳茂波說行政複雜、成本高，市民可能覺得擾民，外地經驗反映對刺激消費作用不大，要再作考慮。<br />\n<br />\n他回應有市民在網上的提問，要求實行全民退保、成立獨立調查委員會和警察凍薪。陳茂波說，暫時沒有計劃推行完全沒有資產審查的全民退保，又說公務員薪酬檢討方面有既定機制。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他重申特首多次表示不適合成立獨立調查委員會，在主持追問下，他強調不會成立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503494-20200118.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503494-20200118.htm&d=qHKTGL1WilUkyN31MLoEKHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=920207ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503494-20200118.htm&h=fa5bbd73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503494-20200118.htm</a>"},{"pid":"67ebbbfb45c41a4f20d4c6a50845e28792ba74d9","tid":1828604,"uid":221051,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:08:32.000Z","msg":"意見分歧？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba576f21bf2a57310317fc4412893395851a6227","tid":1828604,"uid":321803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:09:09.000Z","msg":"班垃圾走返入垃圾桶，唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a734059252fa7409f8b608881dcb5381a794ac8","tid":1828604,"uid":153689,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":